"Starega."

00:36:32.614 --> 00:36:34.014
To je kompliment.

00:36:34.157 --> 00:36:39.496
Vidim zelo prijaznega,
nežnega in modrega starca.

00:36:40.372 --> 00:36:42.165
V domu za ostarele.

00:36:42.916 --> 00:36:44.334
Na vozičku.

