00:37:17.366 --> 00:37:18.909
Vem, da si jezna,
ker misliš,

00:37:18.993 --> 00:37:21.954
da sem te zapustila zaradi
pivo-ponga …

00:37:22.121 --> 00:37:24.498
Nisem rekla, da sem jezna.

00:37:27.083 --> 00:37:30.545
Vem, da si in …

00:37:31.045 --> 00:37:32.445
Nadine.

00:37:33.006 --> 00:37:35.925
Bi rada vedela,
kaj sem opazila ta vikend?

00:37:36.634 --> 00:37:38.034
Seveda.

00:37:38.678 --> 00:37:42.098
Mojbog, Shannon,
srčkana obleka! Res mi je všeč!

00:37:45.352 --> 00:37:46.394
Ja, prav.

00:37:46.561 --> 00:37:48.020
Zato si zavrgla mene?

00:37:48.103 --> 00:37:50.231
Osebo, ki te brani
od drugega razreda?

00:37:50.564 --> 00:37:51.774
Je vedno s tabo.

00:37:51.857 --> 00:37:53.257
Naj bo.
–Tako je bilo.

00:37:53.317 --> 00:37:54.860
Obstaja možnost, da butcem

00:37:54.944 --> 00:37:56.344
ne bo mar zate,

00:37:56.404 --> 00:37:58.739
ko te bo Damien zamenjal
za bolj vročo mačko.

00:38:02.743 --> 00:38:04.143
Pojma nimaš, Nadine.

00:38:05.329 --> 00:38:08.498
Vem, da tega ni lepo slišati,
ampak zgodilo se bo.

00:38:08.665 --> 00:38:10.459
Ne, meni je žal, ne bo se.

00:38:10.625 --> 00:38:14.379
Ker me je tvoj brat pravkar povabil
na maturantski ples.

00:38:19.092 --> 00:38:20.677
Ne.
–Ja, pa me je.

00:38:20.844 --> 00:38:22.930
Pravkar me je povabil.

00:38:25.140 --> 00:38:27.350
Obojega ne moreš imeti.

00:38:27.433 --> 00:38:29.394
Jaz ali on. Izberi.

00:38:30.520 --> 00:38:32.730
Ne, ne bom izbirala.

00:38:32.897 --> 00:38:34.357
Jaz ali on. Hočeš njega?

00:38:34.440 --> 00:38:35.566
Ali mene?
–Nadine.

00:38:35.733 --> 00:38:37.443
To ni izbira.
–Zakaj ne mene?

00:38:37.610 --> 00:38:40.029
On ali jaz, zdaj!
–Ne bom izbirala!

00:38:40.196 --> 00:38:41.596
Potem sva opravili.

