ki je podcenila mojo plačo.

00:51:50.378 --> 00:51:51.796
Dober občutek.

00:51:51.963 --> 00:51:54.131
Ta del.

00:52:06.935 --> 00:52:08.335
Kaj počnete?

00:52:10.272 --> 00:52:12.107
Pol piškota ti bom dal.

00:52:13.400 --> 00:52:14.800
Zakaj?

00:52:16.194 --> 00:52:18.696
Da se boš bolje počutila.
Kristus.

00:52:23.827 --> 00:52:25.227
Veš, kaj?

00:52:26.955 --> 00:52:28.790
Moja najljubša dijakinja si.

00:52:30.166 --> 00:52:31.566
Ti to pomaga?

